<li>Thinking of you and your family during this heartbreaking time.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace during this difficult period.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, we are here for you.</li>
<li>May your cherished memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>Our hearts ache with you in your loss.</li>
<li>Holding you and your family in our thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>We are deeply saddened by your loss. Please accept our sincerest condolences.</li>
